  "remarks": "\nPalestinian Islamic Jihad (PIJ) is a Palestinian Islamist terrorist organization whose has stated that its objective is the destruction of the State of Israel, and which has been responsible for numerous terrorist attacks. PIJ has, through past attacks, demonstrated its willingness to use violence to further its political objectives. The movement has also praised and encouraged violence.",
